[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "少しほろ苦くて、表面はパリッと、\n中はホロホロ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "アンチュ。あなたは何をしていますの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ララ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "なるほど。それで手渡すまでクリセルダには\n内緒にしたいというわけですのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "そのほうが、きちんと気持ちを伝えられると思って……\nでも、一人じゃなかなか上手く作れないの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "手伝って……もらえない、かしら？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。もちろんですわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "もっとも、あちらは面白いことになっている\nようですが……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ねえ。ララ・キングダムでも、リンデ祭に\n何か催しをするの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。全国民にチョコを配ることにしています",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ララならみんなに慕われてるから……\nむしろ全国民からチョコが集まりそうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら。王の慈愛は見返りなど求めていません。\n民は王の庇護を受けていれば良いのです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "そう……なのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "どうかしましたの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "私……この間のお茶会で、嫉妬心を抱いたの。\nクリセルダが誰かのお嫁さんに、なんて思ったら……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "私、クリセルダにただ感謝の気持ちを\n伝えたいだけじゃなくて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "そばにいてほしいから、そんな見返りが欲しいから、\nチョコを渡したいのかもしれない……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それでも良いと思いますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "え、でも……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そんな気持ちを抱かれることを嬉しく思う者も\nいるのですから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（むしろクリセルダなら、間違いなく\n　歓喜しますわね）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "そう……かな？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "私……クリセルダにそばにいてほしい。\nでも、重荷になりたくない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "だから、クリセルダに寄りかかるんじゃなく、\n自分で立って、頼れる私になりたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "そんな気持ちを……\n「ありがとう」って気持ちと一緒に伝えたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。そのまま伝えるのが良いと思いますわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "さぁ、贈りものにふさわしい最高の一品に向けて……\n仕上げといきましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "うん……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]